On the '''General Info''' tab, specify the following settings:[anchor|#_474fa4c3-f6eb-4099-8757-125dbae89ec8] *In the '''Numbering Settings''' section, select the numbering sequences you created on the preparation stage. *In the '''Posting and Retention Settings''' section, specify default source of GL accounts, subaccount masks (if any), and other posting settings. *Fill in the rest of the check boxes as appropriate for your requirements.
